verbose_text: For example, GrTCP2, GrTCP3, GrTCP13b, GrTCP15c, GrTCP19a and GrTCP23 were constitutively expressed in every tissue tested at very high level, implying that these genes may play regulatory roles at multiple development stages, whereas GrTCP6, GrTCP9a, GrTCP20a and GrTCP24 were expressed at very low level in all tissues examined, which suggested that they may be primarily expressed in other organs not tested or under special conditions (XREF_FIG).
